verbose_text: Moreover, some miRNAs (miR-130, miR-27a/b, miR-378 and miR-519d) can directly regulate the levels of two critical transcription factors, peroxisome proliferator activated receptor gamma (PPARgamma) and cytidine-cytidine-adenosine-adenosine-thymidine (CCAAT) enhancer binding protein alpha (C/EBPalpha), thus affecting the dynamics of adipogenesis.
evidence: peroxisome proliferator-activated receptor gamma (PPARgamma) and cytidine-cytidine-adenosine-adenosine-thymidine (CCAAT) enhancer binding protein alpha
